name: Set of 3 Hand Printed Note Cards
description:
These all purpose hand printed cards are perfect for any occasion.  Our family sentiment sets the tone for you to create a personal message inside.  The set of three contains our sweet swimming dog paddling behind a family goslings, our purr-fect kitty following a family of cute chicks and our classic rainbow design.

The set ships with 3 natural colored linen envelopes, all tucked neatly inside a clear cellophane bag.  Each card is folded in half and measures 6" wide by 4.75" tall when folded.  The interior of the cards are left blank for your message.

All images are printed by hand in the USA on heavyweight 50% post consumer recycled paper, using environmentally safe inks.

name: Thank You Armed Forces - womens tee

Navy, 100% cotton, made in the USA.
